Jess is one of the possible Mahogany Homes clients, she lives in East Ardougne on the 1st floor[UK]2nd floor[US] above the pet shop.

Construction contracts[edit | edit source]

Jess is a possible client given to the player by Mahogany Homes, and may ask you to build the following furniture for them, depending on the type of contract that player chose:

Furniture Resources Experience

Drawers (1) 2 planks 45 96 144 224
